msgid ""
"To maintain hotspot functionality during failover, the MAC address of the "
"interface running the hotspot on the primary node is automatically copied to"
" the corresponding interface on the secondary node when a switchover occurs."
" This behavior prevents the use of VLAN interfaces for the hotspot."
msgstr ""
